---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section id="home" class="hero-section d-flex align-items-center" style={`--hero-image: url("${base}images/hero.png")`}>
  <div class="container position-relative">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title text-white mb-3">Altibase Union</h1>
      <p class="hero-copy text-white mb-4">조합원과 함께 만드는 협력의 노사관계</p>
      <div class="hero-values" aria-label="핵심 가치">
        <span><i data-lucide="shield-check" aria-hidden="true"></i>권익 보호</span>
        <span><i data-lucide="messages-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>소통과 참여</span>
        <span><i data-lucide="clipboard-check" aria-hidden="true"></i>투명한 활동</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
